arts for the\nhuman-ventricular TP06 model and have found important differences. In both\nthese models,to make a transition,(from broken-wave to stable-scroll states or\nvice versa) we must simultaneously increase $I_{Kr}$ and decrease $I_{CaL}$;a\nmodification of only one of these currents is not enough to effect this\ntransition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Oct 2020 16:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 14:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
