s in a dispersive microwave propagation environment\nwith respect to the conventional transmission with Nyquist pulse shaping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Oct 2020 04:30:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-25"}
