vent cross-linking from occurring.\nFinally, in a third case, it was found that salts which interacted in an\nintermediate fashion with the polymer (e.g. GndCl) favored the uncollapsed\nconformation at all salt concentrations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Oct 2020 12:37:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-13"}
